### 3. Polyglot.js

[polyglot](https://github.com/airbnb/polyglot.js)，体积小，用法如下：

```js
// 设置所有的字符串
polyglot.extend({
    // pluralization
    "num_cars": "%{smart_count} car |||| %{smart_count} cars",
    "hello": "Hello",
    "hello_name": "Hello, %{name}."
    "nav": {
        "sidebar": {
            "welcome": "Welcome"
        }
    }
});
// 取字符串
polyglot.t("hello_name", {name: "John"});
polyglot.t("nav.sidebar.welcome");
polyglot.locale("de");
```
```html
...

